    <note>Wang(2) Hui [1821] Juzheng's [8145] son, Huaji's [8150] grandson, Juyuan's [1795] nephew, Yue(1)'s [1933] brother, Zhao(1)'s [1773] cousin. His lineage intermarried with the imperial clan, e.g., his father-in-law, Zhao(1) Shoujie [3210], was the eldest son of Zhao(1) Weiji [3215], who was the son of Zhao(1) Taizu's [9001] second son, Dezhao [3214]. His mother-in-law was Wei(5) Renpu's [8157] great granddaughter. XCB, 211.16b, 226.6a; SHY:ZG, 23.9b. CBD, 1, 202.</note>
